  "description": "###  Workflow: Auto-Translate WordPress Posts Using **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)**\n\nThis n8n workflow automates the translation of WordPress blog content into any language using the **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)** API, and inserts the translated text into a Google Doc.\n\n---\n\n## üìå Workflow Steps\n\n1. **Manual Trigger**  \n   Initiates the workflow manually (can be replaced with a webhook or schedule trigger).\n\n2. **WordPress Node**  \n   Retrieves a specific blog post (by ID) from your WordPress site using the REST API.\n\n3. **HTTP Request Node**  \n   Sends the blog content to **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)** via `multipart/form-data`.\n\n4. **Google Docs Node**  \n   Appends the translated text into a specified Google Document using Google Docs API.\n\n---\n\n## üåç API Usage: [**AI Translate Pro**](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)\n\n**Endpoint:**  \n`POST https://ai-translate-pro.p.rapidapi.com/translate.php`\n\n**Content-Type:**  \n`multipart/form-data`\n\n**Required Parameters:**\n\n| Field     | Type   | Description                             |\n|-----------|--------|-----------------------------------------|\n| `text`    | string | The text or HTML content to translate   |\n| `language`| string | Target language (e.g., `Hindi`, `French`) |\n\n**Headers:**\n\n| Header Name         | Value                                 |\n|---------------------|---------------------------------------|\n| `x-rapidapi-host`   | `ai-translate-pro.p.rapidapi.com`     |\n| `x-rapidapi-key`    | Your RapidAPI key                     |\n\n---\n\n## ‚úÖ Benefits of Using **AI Translate Pro**\n\n- ‚ö° **Fast AI-Powered Translation** ‚Äì Instantly translate content with no need for manual input.\n- üåé **Supports Multiple Languages** ‚Äì Easily switch languages to serve global audiences.\n- üß† **Context-Aware** ‚Äì More accurate than basic dictionary translation tools.\n- üõ† **Easy Integration with n8n** ‚Äì No-code/low-code implementation.\n- üóÉ **Content Reuse** ‚Äì Save translations directly into Google Docs for future use or edits.\n- üíº **Cost-Effective** ‚Äì Efficient alternative to expensive manual translation services.\n\n---\n\n## üõ†Ô∏è Problems Solved\n\n- ‚ùå Manual copy-pasting into Google Translate  \n- ‚ùå Limited or slow in-house translation  \n- ‚ùå Difficulty managing multilingual content  \n- ‚ùå Inconsistent formatting or storage  \n- ‚úÖ With **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)**, translations are fast, automated, and saved where your team can access them instantly.\n\n---\n\n## ‚úÖ Example Use Case\n\n- Translate WordPress blog posts from English to Hindi.\n- Store translated content in Google Docs for editing or reuse.\n- Expand to multilingual sites with a simple language switch.\n- Use **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)** in any low-code or no-code platform like n8n.\n\n---\n\n## üìé Requirements\n\n- WordPress REST API credentials\n- RapidAPI access to **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)**\n- Google Docs API service account\n\n---\n\n## üîó More Info\n\nExplore full documentation and pricing on the **[AI Translate Pro](https://rapidapi.com/PrineshPatel/api/ai-translate-pro)** RapidAPI listing page.\n\nCreate your **free n8n account** and set up the workflow in just a few minutes using the link below:\n\nüëâ [Start Automating with n8n](https://n8n.partnerlinks.io/7fuarh1e6dz5)\n\nSave time, stay consistent, and grow your LinkedIn presence effortlessly!\n\n",
